name: G.Skill Trident Z5 RGB 64GB DDR5
description: Premium DDR5 kit (2x32GB) at 6400MHz CL32. Features stunning RGB lighting, Samsung ICs for overclocking headroom, and Intel XMP 3.0 certification.

reviews.review_text: 64GB is perfect for development VMs. Fast and stable.
RGB syncs perfectly with other G.Skill components.
